query:
INSERT INTO
    weather (
    timestamp,latitude,longitude,altitude,wind_speed_10m,wind_direction_10m,air_temperature_2m,relative_humidity_2m,air_pressure_at_sea_level,precipitation_amount,land_area_fraction,cloud_area_fraction
   )
SELECT
    *
FROM
    UNNEST(
        $1::TIMESTAMPTZ[],$2::DECIMAL[],$3::DECIMAL[],$4::DECIMAL[],$5::DECIMAL[],$6::DECIMAL[],$7::DECIMAL[],$8::DECIMAL[],$9::DECIMAL[],$10::DECIMAL[],$11::DECIMAL[],$12::DECIMAL[]
    )
        ON CONFLICT (timestamp,weather_location_id) DO NOTHING
